name: Button Bracelet - The Wise Owl
description:
This bracelet is one of my favorites!

Traditionally, the owl represents wisdom, transition, and protection. In folklore, owls represent wisdom and helpfulness, they are also believed to be prophetic. I've always loved owls and couldn't wait to create a piece to honor these beautiful creatures. 

The bracelet measures 6.5 inches when opened. There are a total of 9 buttons measuring between 7/16 inches to 1 inch. The owl is 1 inch wide and just under 1.5 inches tall.
In addition to the wise owl, there are 2 brass and black colored bottons, 2 silver and blak floral buttons, 2 gold and black bottons, 1 silver flower button and 1 dark silver with a center rhinstone button.

name: Customizable Silk, Brocade or Pleather (fake leather) Clutch
description:
This is a completely customizable clutch. Perfect for weddings or an evening out.

This isn't your typical clutch sized purse; it's roomy enough to hold a checkbook size wallet, keys, and cell phone, with room to spare for cosmetics. 

Makes a great gift for bridesmaids.


As with any purse I make just for you, I will ask what colors and types of fabrics you are interested in. If you happen to have a color sample I'll probably ask you to send it to me so I can bring it with me to the fabric store. I will go to the fabric store and get fabric specifiaclly for you.


If there is a specific material you have in mind, please let me know. If you already have fabric you'd like made into a clutch, let me know- we can decide on a fair price together.

Goes from a wide point of a 10 1/2" body to the top of the bag at 8" 

Depth of the bag is 5”, with a total height of the bag at 6 1/2"

Price is per clutch. To inquire about placing a customized order, contact me.
